Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:18.40,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:29.86,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:36.79,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:47.92,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:56.85,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:08.74,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:20.63,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:26.47,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:36.27,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:29.86,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:36.79,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:47.92,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:56.85,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:08.74,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:20.63,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:26.47,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:36.27,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:56.78,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(500,415)}Ep. 39 - Two Partings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:13.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Snowflake. If the goats are giving us milk,\Nwhy aren't you giving any?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:19.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me! Hey! Hey!
Comment: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:32.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:35.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:40.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:44.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little... So Lucy returned already, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:52.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I giving Little some exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:56.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate was looking for you a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:59.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I bet she wants to make me study again or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:02.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Finally on my summer vacation,\Nstudying is the last thing I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:05.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about studying.\NShe said it's something about Snowflake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,About Snowflake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:07.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:14.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What about Snowflake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:15.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:18.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense. I guess I won't be able\Nto learn anything from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:21.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When autumn comes, I'll go to school too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:22.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Pure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're an odd fellow, Tob.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:29.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I ride this hammock too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:30.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:32.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty tired from all this\Nrunning around with Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sister, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:36.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:36.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:37.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch-ouch-ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:43.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did I tell you? Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:48.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this hammock?\NYou propped it up, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:48.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:51.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When you do that, at least prop it tightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you climb it slowly, it'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:56.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:01.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:07.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Cooking is nowhere near as exciting\Nwhen you're doing it without any meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did meat really become that expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:13.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The meat-yielding animals\Nsuch as cows, pigs, and sheep are very sparse here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:16.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the population\Nof Southern Australia increased greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:18.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we see a lot of sheep around...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:22.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. But they only\Nkeep the sheep for their wool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:29.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I sure would love to stuff myself\Nwith some delectable meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:32.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, we might soon be able to do that.\NBut for now, just try to bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:36.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, unless we have the money,\Nwe can't buy any expensive meat, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:41.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And dad can't go to work yet,\Neven if his leg healed up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:43.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It hadn't fully recovered yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:47.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But the other day, I heard Doctor Deighton\Ntelling dad it's already fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:52.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If dad starts working again,\Nwe can buy meat and whatever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:53.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:59.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you already?\NDad's leg hadn't fully recovered yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:01.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,One way or another, he drinks too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:20.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm almost out of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:22.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't harm your health\Nfurthermore by drinking so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not drinking {\i1}that{\i0} much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you start even such\Na bright morning from drinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Before long, it'll be evening again, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:35.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that dad was drinking too much as of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:37.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There was something deeply frustrating about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:43.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad was now drinking even more\Nthan Dr. Deighton, an inveterate drunkard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:49.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Doctor Deighton!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Well met, Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:56.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:58.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You've finished working already, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:05:59.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Going on a date tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We've met you at a perfect time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:04.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:09.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Clara was awfully worried lately,\Nso she even came to ask for my advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:11.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Advice? What in the world is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's about my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:15.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My father won't stop drinking these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so that's how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:24.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how father feels\Nand why that makes him want to drink more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:27.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But by drinking so much,\Nhe'll ruin his health for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:30.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He still can't get any land,\Nadd to that his leg injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:35.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because nothing ever goes according to plan,\NMr. Popple resorted to drinking alcohol, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:37.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That must definitely be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:40.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If as Clara says, he'll ruin his health,\Nthat'd be a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:46.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, drinking that much\Nwon't be enough to ruin his health.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:51.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at me, who's been drinking for most of my life,\Nyet my health is still more or less excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:55.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound like something\Na doctor should say!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:58.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But well, I was just telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're still in favor of drinking, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:06.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I suppose, Mr. Popple is drinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:08.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be better for him to hold back a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:10.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:13.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We no longer have any money at all in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's been two months since father last worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:19.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, I've begun\Nfreeloading at your place again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:24.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My and Ben's salaries are totally not enough\Nto keep our family going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:30.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I also thought I'd go talk to Mr. Popple,\Nask him to stop drinking and start working again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:34.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, if only you can,\Nplease help us persuade him. I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm such a drunkard myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:41.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,if I'd tell another to cut back on drinking,\Nmy words won't have any weight to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll try to hint it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:43.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I would really appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:49.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. By the way, in two or three days,\Nmy stay in your house will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:54.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But then, where are you going next, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:59.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've settled on going to a medical office\Nin the newly built city of Gawler.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.47,0:08:01.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,City of Gawler?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:03.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Adelaide is pretty well-supplied with doctors now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:07.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But in Gawler, they've not a single Doctor yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:10.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Which means we won't get to see you\Nfor a long while, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And when are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:17.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's very sudden news.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:20.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We agreed on them\Nsending over a carriage for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:25.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Having to part with you sure is sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have a drink, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:28.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:29.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not drinking today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:32.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I'm just not in the mood for drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:40.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't sound like your usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:44.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I'm cutting back\Non drinking from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:46.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,For my health's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:50.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,John, will you drink with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:51.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:52.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:53.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, join me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:56.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:01.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you two?\NThat's very strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:03.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:04.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:07.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you, please, stop drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:11.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,However you look at it,\N{\i1}this{\i0} much is {\i1}too{\i0} much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:15.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your feelings,\Nthe frustration that's tormenting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:22.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My feelings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:26.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even if she doesn't say anything,\Nmom is very worried too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:32.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:35.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:39.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Drinking alcohol didn't make me\Nmuch happier anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:40.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for causing you so much worry.
Comment: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:49.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:05.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? They're going to eat Snowflake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:07.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I said it's probably a joke, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:09.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's horrible even as a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:14.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing we don't have to worry about is the goat's milk. It's coming out really nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:19.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Kate, is our family actually {\i1}that{\i0} destitute?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:22.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems. We've completely ran out of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:25.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What'll become of us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:30.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If dad starts working again,\Nwe'll pull through, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:48.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:51.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As always, sticking close to Snowflake, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:55.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:58.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:03.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I came back with Clara and John.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:04.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:05.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:07.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:09.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you've not drank anything today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:10.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:13.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now isn't that unusual?\NDad didn't drink either?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:14.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:16.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:19.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, are you unwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:22.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Me? No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:23.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:27.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I have my reasons. Right.\NFor the next three days, I'm not drinking anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:28.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why three days, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:35.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the city of Gawler\Nto work at the doctor's office there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:38.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it comes with a free dwelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:39.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll have to part?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Gawler is pretty far, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:42.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:44.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we may come visit you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:45.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:48.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't me lying here?\NI'm getting pretty exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:49.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Comment: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:53.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Doctor, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:57.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:11:58.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:01.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:05.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, didn't I tell you to be careful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:06.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I didn't expect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:10.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:12.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta climb on it slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:14.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:16.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Slowly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:20.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it sure is comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:30.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:31.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:34.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please give my regard to Ben as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:36.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, farewell, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:37.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll come visit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting.
Comment: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:42.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we may go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:45.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Giddyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:13:00.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Doctor! Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:13.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Since our arrival to Southern Australia,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:19.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Deighton became part of the family for us.\NAnd now he left for the city of Gawler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:23.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What a truly tragic parting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I protest! I decisively protest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:14:01.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I brought Snowflake up myself!\NBesides, her and Little made great friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:04.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We knew you'd probably say just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:06.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But dear, please hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:08.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We no longer have any money whatsoever in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:13.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So, because we don't have any urgent need in her,\Nwe wanted to put her out on the next town auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:16.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Anything but Snowflake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:21.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Lucy. I want you to think of it:\Nthere's no point in keeping just one sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:25.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we shear her, one sheep's wool\Nisn't enough for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:28.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying Snowflake is of no use to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:29.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, on the contrary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:34.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It can be of great use to us.\NAbove all, we could use her for meat that we can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:35.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:38.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:41.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because we've known Snowflake ever since\Nshe was a baby, we can't do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:45.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Just let Snowflake stay in our house\Nthe way she lives here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:49.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The goats are good for milking them. But that sheep...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Snowflake has a very soft wool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:55.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just touching her wool\Nis greatly pleasing to the senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:57.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't put that to any use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:59.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little... Little will feel very lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:05.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We kept Snowflake so as to get Little used to being\Naround sheep without attacking them, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:09.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We got it from Mr. Long, the shepherd!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:13.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little is now perfectly used to being around sheep.\NSeemingly, not one bit interested in attacking them. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:17.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Which means Snowflake\Nalready fulfilled her role, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:21.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't want to part with Snowflake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please come to see the reason, Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's you who is being unreasonable here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:32.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, isn't there anything else suitable for selling,\Nother than that sheep? Let's think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:36.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:45.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father and the others are having a hard time, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We really don't have any more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:54.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, starting this Monday,\Ndad starts working at road construction again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:57.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we no longer need to sell Snowflake off, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:04.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Lucy, what if we swallow the bitter pill\Nand sell Snowflake?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:09.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even you say we have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:13.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I just think that for the good of our family,\Nwe'd better sell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:16.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't only think about yourself here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:28.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid, do you happen to know\Nwhere Mr. Popple's house is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:29.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here? Much obliged.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:44.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Mr. Popple! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone home?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:48.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They should be in the backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:49.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Backyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:51.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, what did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You live in this house, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:53.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:57.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I came here to take a look at the sheep.\NIf I like it, I might buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? It's in the backyard too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Show me the way, kid, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:03.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:11.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They came to buy the sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:16.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I called from the doorway,\Nbut you couldn't hear me, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? It's that sheep?
Comment: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:25.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:28.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This one doesn't look half-bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:30.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Madam. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:31.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:35.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but who was it\Nwho told you about this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:37.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why, it was your husband, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:41.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I met him at the town market,\Nwhere he asked if I would like to buy a sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:47.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, we've decided not to sell Snowflake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:50.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right... Instead of selling Snowflake,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:54.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,we decided to raise money by selling my clothes\Nand the clothes that you girls outgrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:57.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared to fork out two pounds for this sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Two pounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:02.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,By selling clothes, you could raise\Nten shillings at best, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But this sheep...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:10.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, we can by no means sell Snowflake!\NDad also said we don't need to sell it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:15.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. There's probably been\Na conflict of opinions somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:17.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry for turning you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:20.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's a shame.\NThis one is an actually good sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:27.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,With two pounds, we'd probably be\Nwell off for some while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:32.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But if you've returned to working,\Nwe don't need those two pounds, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:36.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't necessarily imply\Nthere will always be job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:38.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But that sheep...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:42.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If we explain it really well to Lucy,\Nshe'll probably also come to see the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So we're not selling these clothes for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:48.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They'd probably only be one fifth or one sixth\Nof what a sheep would yield.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:52.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How should we bring it to Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:56.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure it's tomorrow\Nwhen they're holding the auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:33.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Don't you startle me like that, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:34.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:36.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:39.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:50.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Go play with Snowflake in the backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:53.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:01.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where are the clothes that were here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:03.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Arthur took them to the auction grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:05.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he gets good deals for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:06.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:08.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:09.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:21.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Little? That was pretty loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:34.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, where did Snowflake go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:39.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Snowflake is not in the backyard, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:44.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Arthur took her to the auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No way... No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:51.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm sorry. But that was\Nthe only option we had left!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:55.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel! Awfully cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:21:59.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.39,0:22:03.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To bring her back from the auction grounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:05.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:11.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Cruel. So cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:22.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone, a splendid sheep we got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.41,0:22:27.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good both for shearing and for butchering!\NA remarkable sheep, however you look at it! 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:31.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start the bidding at one pound!\NRight! One pound!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:33.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,One pound! One pound! One pound!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:34.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pound and a half!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:37.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At once, we hear a bid of a pound and a half!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:40.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pound and a half! Alright, it's a pound and a half!\NOne pound and a half!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:41.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Two pounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.51,0:22:43.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Two pounds! Two pounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:46.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Any more bids? Two pounds for this amazing sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:47.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, will we hear one more bid?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:49.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! Two pounds and a half!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:52.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Two and a half! Two and a half!\NA two and a half pounds bid was made!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:22:59.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:03.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.83,0:23:05.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:11.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lucy! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:29.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A runaway horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.12,0:23:32.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A runaway horse! A runaway horse, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:33.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Run for your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:38.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dodge it to the right! To the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:53.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's heading towards the city center!\NStop it, someone! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:07.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When I came to my senses, I found myself\Nin an unfamiliar luxurious mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.30,0:24:11.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to remember where I used to live before\Nor even what my name was.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.49,0:24:14.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Lucy-May of the Southern Rainbow:\N"Who am I?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.89,0:24:16.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
